"48:6:1" : {s: 48, a: 6, w: 1, r: "عذب", t: "وَيُعَذِّبَ", l: "عَذَّبَ", lc: 41, tl: "wayuʿadhiba", lb: "শাস্তি দেওয়া, আযাব দেওয়া",e: "And He (may) punish", b: "", i: "dan Dia hendak mengazab", f: 2, rm: "chastisement, castigate, punishment, torture, torment, retribution, abstain/desist (e.g. from eating due to excessive thirst), relinquish, quit. To deny a thing, hinder anyone from, be inaccessible, prevent.", ag: "واو عطف وفعل مضارع صيغة ٢", eg: "Conjunction wa and Verb Imperfect 2nd form", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "IMPF", qual: "(II)", deg: "3", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "SUBJ", lu: "عَذَابٌ،يُعَذِّبُ"},
"48:6:2" : {s: 48, a: 6, w: 2, r: "نفق", t: "ٱلْمُنَٰفِقِينَ", l: "مُنَٰفِقُون", lc: 27, tl: "l-munāfiqīna", lb: "খরচকারী, ব্যয়কারী",e: "the hypocrite men", b: "", i: "orang-orang munafik laki-laki", f: 15, rm: "to be saleable, to come out of a hole, be exhausted (store), consumed, spent, expenditure. To enter into another hole where there is another outlet, so is a hypocrite who professes to believe first one thing and then another, thus entering faith through one door and leaving it through another.", ag: "ال التعريف وأسم فاعل", eg: "Determiner al and Noun Active participle", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "ACT_PCPL", qual: "ACC", deg: "", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "أَنفَقَ،مُنَٰفِقُونَ"},
"48:6:3" : {s: 48, a: 6, w: 3, r: "نفق", t: "وَٱلْمُنَٰفِقَٰتِ", l: "مُنَٰفِقَٰت", lc: 5, tl: "wal-munāfiqāti", lb: "মুনাফিক নারী",e: "and the hypocrite women", b: "", i: "dan orang-orang munafik perempuan", f: 3, rm: "to be saleable, to come out of a hole, be exhausted (store), consumed, spent, expenditure. To enter into another hole where there is another outlet, so is a hypocrite who professes to believe first one thing and then another, thus entering faith through one door and leaving it through another.", ag: "واو عطف وال التعريف وأسم فاعل", eg: "Conjunction wa and Determiner al and Noun Active participle", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "ACT_PCPL", qual: "ACC", deg: "", gen: "F", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "أَنفَقَ،مُنَٰفِقُونَ"},
"48:6:4" : {s: 48, a: 6, w: 4, r: "شرك", t: "وَٱلْمُشْرِكِينَ", l: "مُشْرِك", lc: 44, tl: "wal-mush'rikīna", lb: "মুশরিক, যে আল্লাহর সাথে অংশীদার সাব্যস্ত করে, শিরককারী, অংশীদার স্থাপনকারী",e: "and the polytheist men", b: "", i: "dan orang-orang musyrik laki-laki", f: 4, rm: "to be a companion, be sharer/partner. shirkun - share, participation, polytheism, idolatry, making associate/partner with Allah. shariik (pl. shurakaa) - associate, partner, sharer. Nouns of the second declension when followed by the affixed pronouns take the three inflexions thus shurakaa, shurakaai, shurakaaa. shaarak (vb. 3) - to share with. ashraka (vb. 4) - to make a sharer or associate, give companions (e.g. to God), be a polytheist or idolater. ashraktumuuni - you associated me as partner. mushrik - one who gives associate to God, polytheist. mushtarikun (vb. 8) - one who partakes or shares.", ag: "واو عطف وال التعريف وأسم فاعل", eg: "Conjunction wa and Determiner al and Noun Active participle", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "ACT_PCPL", qual: "ACC", deg: "", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "أَشْرَكَ،شُرَكَآءُ،شُرَكَٰٓؤُا۟،يُشْرِكُ"},
"48:6:5" : {s: 48, a: 6, w: 5, r: "شرك", t: "وَٱلْمُشْرِكَٰتِ", l: "مُشْرِكَٰت", lc: 3, tl: "wal-mush'rikāti", lb: "মুশরিক নারী",e: "and the polytheist women", b: "", i: "dan orang-orang musyrik perempuan", f: 2, rm: "to be a companion, be sharer/partner. shirkun - share, participation, polytheism, idolatry, making associate/partner with Allah. shariik (pl. shurakaa) - associate, partner, sharer. Nouns of the second declension when followed by the affixed pronouns take the three inflexions thus shurakaa, shurakaai, shurakaaa. shaarak (vb. 3) - to share with. ashraka (vb. 4) - to make a sharer or associate, give companions (e.g. to God), be a polytheist or idolater. ashraktumuuni - you associated me as partner. mushrik - one who gives associate to God, polytheist. mushtarikun (vb. 8) - one who partakes or shares.", ag: "واو عطف وال التعريف وأسم فاعل", eg: "Conjunction wa and Determiner al and Noun Active participle", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "ACT_PCPL", qual: "ACC", deg: "", gen: "F", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "أَشْرَكَ،شُرَكَآءُ،شُرَكَٰٓؤُا۟،يُشْرِكُ"},
